reviewText:
First of all, this game is freaking awesome. I've been looking to play games like this since, I don't know, a pretty long time. Essentially, you play as a dragon created by men, to defeat other dragons. Sounds fantastic now, doesn't it? Let me list some of the pros and cons.

pros:
- You play as a dragon;
- You play as a gun-wielding dragon;
- You play as a dragon with a cannon on its back;
- You play as a dragon;
- Gameplay mechanics are quite fun;

cons:
- Delay time (?)
I need the devs to clarify this. I don't know if its just me, but the delay time for me is quite ridiculous. I accidentally
pressed  ` " in the middle of the game which resulted in a pop up window (basically pause popup with continue and
quit) that could not be closed even after I clicked like a dozen time. Also
